Product Type: Includes instruments, consumables, and accessories.
Test Type: Covers stool examination, blood tests, imaging tests, tumor markers, biopsies, and other diagnostic methods.
Cancer Stages: Divided into Stage 0, Stage I, Stage II, Stage III, and Stage IV.
Cancer Type: Encompasses adenocarcinoma, colorectal lymphoma, gastrointestinal stromal tumors, carcinoid tumors, and others.
Age Group: Segments include geriatric, adult, and pediatric populations.
End User: Includes hospitals, diagnostic centers, cancer research centers, ambulatory surgical centers, academic institutes, and other stakeholders.
